<p>Taken many online surveys? What’s that experience been like?  Befuddling at times?</p>
<p>Many CX surveys are very effective. They hit the mark. Yet others are sorely lacking. Great surveys add to the customer experience while poorly designed surveys reflect negatively on the brands that sponsor them. And worse yet, they can be annoying.</p>
<p>With Qualtrics, you can craft insightful and appealing surveys that customers are happy to complete. You’ll gather critical information to drive your business forward. And you’ll devise visualizations that clearly display the relevant insights.</p>
<p>In this section:</p>
<ul>
<li>Adding &amp; Customizing Common Question Types</li>
<li>Adding &amp; Importing Advanced Questions</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>

